**********************************************************************
MAUI Device Capability Information demo code
**********************************************************************
What this demo does:
  - The demo looks in the CDB for each graphics device name and prints 
    all information about each graphics device capabilities, including 
    resolutions and coding methods supported.

**********************************************************************
System requirements:
  - A working MAUI environment is assumed.
 
**********************************************************************
Directories: 
  - Source code 
      $MWOS/SRC/MAUI/DEMOS/GXDEVCAP
        
**********************************************************************
To make this demo:
  - From the source file directory type:
      % os9make
 
**********************************************************************
Operation:
 
  - This demo has no command line options. To run simply type the
    demo name. The shell prompt will return after the demo ends.

      $ gxdevcap

**********************************************************************
 
